keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map <space>o Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map <space>p Vomnibar.activate
map <space>; Vomnibar.activate
map <space>P Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map <space>d duplicateTab
map <space>w removeTab
map <space>W restoreTab
map <space>r restoreTab
map <space>y restoreTab
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map <space>j goBack
map <space>k goForward
